  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 44ff468522a88594f835ce1750834844, type: 3}
  m_Name: Reaction
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  dialogue:
  - Here is the reaction menu.
  - You have the option of attempting to dodge the enemy attack and take no damage.
  - You can also try to counter and hit them back instead.
  - However, these actions will also use EN.
  - You may also choose to just "tank" and get hit normally, if you deem it necessary.
  - For this example, let's counter.
